---
title: Pricing - Flexible and affordable | Vehicle Detailing ( Holmfirth, UK )
---

<a name="pricing"></a>
<div>
  <div class="ab-plans-section-text  mdl-typography--text-center">
    <div class="mdl-typography--font-light  mdl-typography--display-2-color-contrast">Pricing for everyone</div>
    <p class="mdl-typography--font-light">I can tailor a bespoke care package for your needs.
    </p>
    <p> The possibilities are endless and may include part of a package, a single package or a combination of processes from each package.
    </p>
    <p>Contact me to arrange a free assessment &amp; to discuss your needs. </p>

    <div class="mdl-grid">
        <div class="mdl-cell mdl-cell--4-col mdl-cell--3-col-desktop mdl-cell--3-offset-desktop mdl-cell--4-col-tablet">
            <div class="mdl-typography--display-1-color-contrast">


          <a href="#cars">
            <button class="mdl-button mdl-js-button mdl-button--raised mdl-js-ripple-effect mdl-button--accent">

              <i class="fa fa-car fa-lg fa-fw"></i>
  Car Pricing
            </button>
          </a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mdl-cell mdl-cell--6-col mdl-cell--3-col-desktop mdl-cell--4-col-tablet">
            <div class="mdl-typography--display-1-color-contrast">

          <a href="#motorbikes">
            <button class="mdl-button mdl-js-button mdl-button--raised mdl-js-ripple-effect mdl-button--accent">

              <i class="fa fa-motorcycle fa-lg fa-fw"></i>
  Motorbike Pricing
            </button>
          </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>
<a name="cars"></a>
<div class="ab-plans-section">
  <div class="mdl-typography--text-center">
    <div class="mdl-typography--font-light mdl-typography--display-1-color-contrast">Pricing for Cars</div>
    <div class="mdl-grid ab-card-container">

      <% data.pricing.cars.each do |p| %>
      <div class="mdl-cell mdl-card mdl-shadow--4dp ab-card">

        <div class="mdl-card__title">
          <h2 class="mdl-typography--text-center mdl-card__title-text "><i class="fa fa-car ">&nbsp;</i><%= p.title %></h2>
        </div>
        <div class="mdl-card__media">
          <div class="mdl-typography--text-center mdl-typography--display-3 mdl-typography--font-thin"><span class="mdl-typography--display-1 mdl-typography--font-thin">from</span> £<%= p.price %></div>
          <p class="mdl-typography--headline mdl-typography--font-thin"><%= p.strapline %></p>
        </div>

        <div class="mdl-card__actions">

          <a href="#contact">
            <button class="ab-button mdl-button mdl-js-button mdl-button--raised mdl-js-ripple-effect">
              <i class="material-icons">call</i>
            contact
            </button>
          </a>

        </div>
        <div class="mdl-card__supporting-text  mdl-typography--text-left">
          <ul class="mdl-list">
            <% p.jobs.each do |j| %>
            <li class="mdl-list__item">
              <span class="mdl-list__item-primary-content">
                  <i class="material-icons mdl-list__item-icon"><%= j.icon %></i>
                  <%= j.name %>
                </span>
            </li>
            <% end %>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <% end %>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<a name="motorbikes"></a>
<div class="ab-plans-section">
  <div class="mdl-typography--text-center">
    <div class="mdl-typography--font-light mdl-typography--display-1-color-contrast">Pricing for Motorbikes</div>
    <div class="mdl-grid ab-card-container">

      <% data.pricing.bikes.each do |p| %>
      <div class="mdl-cell mdl-card mdl-shadow--4dp ab-card">

        <div class="mdl-card__title">
          <h2 class="mdl-typography--text-center mdl-card__title-text "><i class="fa fa-motorcycle">&nbsp;</i><%= p.title %></h2>
        </div>
        <div class="mdl-card__media">
          <div class="mdl-typography--text-center mdl-typography--display-3 mdl-typography--font-thin"><span class="mdl-typography--display-1 mdl-typography--font-thin">from</span> £<%= p.price %></div>
          <p class="mdl-typography--headline mdl-typography--font-thin"><%= p.strapline %></p>
        </div>

        <div class="mdl-card__actions">

          <a href="#contact">
            <button class="ab-button mdl-button mdl-js-button mdl-button--raised mdl-js-ripple-effect">
              <i class="material-icons">call</i>
            contact
            </button>
          </a>

        </div>
        <div class="mdl-card__supporting-text  mdl-typography--text-left">
          <ul class="mdl-list">
            <% p.jobs.each do |j| %>
            <li class="mdl-list__item">
              <span class="mdl-list__item-primary-content">
                  <i class="material-icons mdl-list__item-icon"><%= j.icon %></i>
                  <%= j.name %>
                </span>
            </li>
            <% end %>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <% end %>

    </div>

  </div>


</div>

